{
  "id": "69c3d2e17e75e234184dee69",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:メモの死蔵問題",
  "created": 1774441218,
  "updated": 1774441240,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c3d2e17e75e234184dee69",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:メモの死蔵問題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441218,
      "updated": 1774441218
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30100000000000ca5e3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441218,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e4",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日のテーマは〜“[メモの死蔵問題]”！つまり、メモ取ったのに見返さずに墓入りしがち問題ね。あるあるすぎて草w じゃ、さっそくいこー！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e7",
      "text": "「まあ……せっかく書き留めた言葉たちが、静かに眠り続けてしまうのは、どこか寂しゅうございますね（微笑）。まるで読まれぬ手紙のようですわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5e9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ea",
      "text": "「定義しておく。“メモの死蔵”とは、記録した情報が再利用されない状態。ナレッジマネジメントの失敗例の一つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5eb",
      "text": "原因は主に三つ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ec",
      "text": " 1. 検索性の低さ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ed",
      "text": " 2. 整理構造の欠如、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ee",
      "text": " 3. 再訪トリガーの不在",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ef",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f2",
      "text": "「出た出た、りかの三段コンボw でもさ、ぶっちゃけ“どこに書いたか忘れた”が9割じゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f5",
      "text": "「否定しない。人間の記憶はインデックスが曖昧。だから外部記憶＝メモには検索可能性が必須。例えばタグ付けやフルテキスト検索」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f8",
      "text": "「探せぬ本は、持っていないのと同じ……ということですのね。書庫の奥にしまい込んだままでは、知識も息ができませんわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5fa",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5fb",
      "text": "「うまいこと言うじゃん、お姉さま！でもタグとか言われてもさ〜、最初はやる気あるけど途中でめんどくさくなって放置コースなんよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5fd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5fe",
      "text": "「その問題は“運用コストの過多”。解決策は“最低限ルール”。例えば“1メモ1テーマ＋2タグまで”など制約を設ける」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca5ff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca600",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca601",
      "text": "「お、なんかゲームの縛りプレイみたいでいいじゃん。それなら続けられそう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca602",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca603",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca604",
      "text": "「人は、あまりにも自由であると、かえって迷ってしまうものですものね。小さな枠が、やさしく導いてくれることもあります（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca605",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca606",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca607",
      "text": "「加えて、“再訪の仕組み”も必要。いわゆるリマインダーや定期レビュー。例えば週1で“メモ見返しタイム”を設定する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca608",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca609",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60a",
      "text": "「それ、通知来ても普通にスルーしそうなんだがw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60d",
      "text": "「対策：レビューを“タスク化”ではなく“イベント化”。例えば“お菓子食べながら振り返る時間”にする」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca60f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca610",
      "text": "「それは神アイデア。報酬つきイベントは参加率バグるやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca611",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca612",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca613",
      "text": "「楽しみと結びつけることで、習慣はやわらかく根づいていくのですね。まるで、しおりを挟むように日々に寄り添って……（少し考える）あら、少し詩的すぎましたかしら」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca614",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca615",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca616",
      "text": "「いや全然、むしろエモい！採用！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca617",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca618",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca619",
      "text": "「もう一点。“アウトプット前提のメモ”にする。つまり、書いたら誰かに話す、まとめる、投稿する。用途があると死蔵しにくい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61c",
      "text": "「わかる〜！人に話す予定あると、ちゃんと整理するもんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca61f",
      "text": "「誰かに伝えることを思えば、言葉も自然と磨かれていきますものね。それは、書き手にとっても喜びでございます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca620",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca621",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca622",
      "text": "「エビデンスとしては、“生成効果（generation effect）”がある。自分で情報を生成・再構成すると記憶保持が向上するというもの",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca623",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generation_effect",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca624",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca625",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca626",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca627",
      "text": "「おお、ちゃんと裏取りしてくるのえらい。さすが技術担当」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca628",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca629",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62a",
      "text": "「まとめる。メモの死蔵を防ぐには――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62b",
      "text": " 検索しやすくする（タグ・一元化）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62c",
      "text": " シンプルな運用ルール",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62d",
      "text": " 定期的な再訪",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62e",
      "text": " アウトプット前提",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca62f",
      "text": "以上」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca630",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca631",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca632",
      "text": "「はい、テストに出まーす！ってやつねw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca633",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca634",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca635",
      "text": "「けれど、たとえ忘れられたとしても、その時に書いたという行為自体が、心に何かを残しているのかもしれませんね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca636",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca637",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca638",
      "text": "「うわ、それちょっと救われるやつ…でもまあ、せっかくだし蘇らせていこ！ゾンビメモ復活祭！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca639",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63b",
      "text": "「ネーミングは不穏だが、コンセプトは正しい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63e",
      "text": "「にぎやかで、少し楽しそうでもありますね（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca63f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca640",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca641",
      "text": "「よーし、今週から“おやつレビュー会”開催決定〜！りか、システム設計よろしく！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca642",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca643",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca644",
      "text": "「了解。プロトコルを構築する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca645",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca646",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3d30300000000000ca647",
      "text": "「お茶もご用意いたしますね。穏やかな振り返りの時間になりますように（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774441219,
      "updated": 1774441219
    },
